=== 奖项 ===
在2014年，308击败宝马i3和[[特斯拉S型|特斯拉S型]]荣获[[欧洲年度风云车|欧洲年度风云车]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Mann|first=Richard|title=New Peugeot 308 wins European Car of the Year 2014|url=http://www.chartersgroup.com/peugeot/news/euro-car-of-the-year-2014-is-the-peugeot-308/|publisher=Charters|accessdate=2014-03-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304010512/http://www.chartersgroup.com/peugeot/news/euro-car-of-the-year-2014-is-the-peugeot-308/|archivedate=2014-03-04}}</ref>。同年，标致308也由意大利汽车记者协会评为当年“欧洲汽车”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uiga.marinaterpolilli.com/premio%20uiga%20auto%20europa%202015%20peugeot%20308|title=Peugeot 308, Car of the year 2015 in Italy|date=|accessdate=2014-12-20|publisher=Union Italiana Giornalisti Automobile dell'Automotive|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109161845/http://uiga.marinaterpolilli.com/premio%20uiga%20auto%20europa%202015%20peugeot%20308|archivedate=2014-11-09}}</ref>。并同年由“施韦策画报”等四本汽车杂志评为瑞士年度汽车<ref>{{cite web|last=|first=|title=Peugeot 308 : Das "Schweizer Auto des Jahres"|url=http://www.blick.ch/auto/news_n_trends/schon-getestet-das-schweizer-auto-des-jahres-peugeot-308-ein-siegertyp-id2564085.html|publisher=Charters|accessdate=2014-12-20|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019061023/https://www.blick.ch/auto/news_n_trends/schon-getestet-das-schweizer-auto-des-jahres-peugeot-308-ein-siegertyp-id2564085.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

